metadata.name: Cocoa Love
metadata.description: Delicious artisan chocolates delivered to your door (Within the US and Canada); an NFT you can eat! Handmade in small batches with primarily organic ingredients and no preservatives, these chocolates are a delectable work of art. This box contains fresh-made decadent chocolates, both dark and milk varieties. The perfect Valentine gift for anyone who loves luscious, rich chocolates (and NFTs).
